txt.en: 'Defeating the Warg champions will do much to hobble the enemy.'

'Good work, brother. The names of the most vicious and ferocious of the Wargs were on the missive you retrieved. The winner of these trials is given a prized skull, which at this moment is in Rung-shakam. You are going to steal that skull, and bring it to the dens of Nazdrau and Sulthrug. The prize will draw them out, and they may be caught unawares.'
Plant the skull trophy and defeat Nazdrau
Plant the skull trophy and defeat Sulthrug
The skull trophy is located in Rung-shakam.\n\nYou should steal the skull trophy.

The den of Sulthrug can be found in western Azanulbizar.\n\nYou should plant the skull trophy before Sulthrug's den.
'You have defeated both monsters? Excellent! We have dealt a stinging blow to the enemy this day.'
